## Summary
This documentation covers the installation and configuration of Session Replay using Android SDK middleware for apps already instrumented with the maintenance Amplitude SDK (2.40.1+). It details initialization, configuration options like sampling rate, data masking, user opt-out, and methods to control recording during sensitive app sections.

